> {%
    client.global.set("token", response.body.data);
%}

### 1. 查列表 —— 期望 code=0，data 是数组
GET http://localhost:8000/api/resonators
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 2. 查单个（存在的 id）—— 期望 code=0，data 是对象
GET http://localhost:8000/api/resonators/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 3. 新增 —— 期望 code=0，data 里有自增回填的 id；createdAt 是北京时间
POST http://localhost:8000/api/resonators
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "name": "测试",
  "element": "热熔",
  "star": 5,
  "level": 80,
  "resonanceChain": 0
}